## ğŸ§± PART 3 â€” Struct Modeling Exercises

### **Exercise S1 â€” Player Model**
```swift
struct Player {
    var name: String
    var score: Int
}
```
Store players in a `@State` array and list them.

---

### **Exercise S2 â€” Task Model**
```swift
struct Task {
    var title: String
    var isCompleted: Bool
}
```
Display tasks in a list with toggles bound to each task.

---

### **Exercise S3 â€” Card Model**
```swift
struct Card {
    var title: String
    var detail: String
    var isFavorite: Bool
}
```
Render the cards in a styled VStack.

